comments: Valanciunas (NOP) engages with Jokic (DEN) as they each attempt to establish rebounding position and marginal contact occurs as Valanciunas disengages, including some made to Jokic's head. Contact to an opponent's head/face can be deemed marginal when the result of a natural basketball move, provided the contact is not disproportionate or uncontrolled.
Jokic (DEN) raises his arm in pursuit of the rebound and marginal contact occurs with Valanciunas' (NOP) left arm as Valanciunas gains control of the ball.
Valanciunas (NOP) extends into Jokic's (DEN) path and initiates body contact during the drive.
After disengaging with one another inside the perimeter, Green (DEN) moves forward toward Hernangomez (NOP) and marginal contact occurs with Hernangomez's back as he receives the pass.
McCollum (NOP) establishes himself in a screening position in Gordon's (DEN) path and absorbs the contact.
Rivers (DEN) brings his hands toward Ingram's (NOP) path and marginal contact occurs as Ingram drives inside the perimeter.
Rivers (DEN) is retreating his left hand away when he brushes Ingram's (NOP) right arm as Ingram starts his upward shooting motion. Rivers avoids making any further contact with Ingram thereafter.
Jokic (DEN) establishes himself in a screening position in Jones' (NOP) path and marginal contact occurs to Jones' side as Jokic turns to roll.
Snell (NOP) and Hernangomez (NOP) legally contest Morris' (DEN) driving shot attempt.
Morris (DEN) wraps Snell's (NOP) upper half with both arms off-ball.
Green's (DEN) left arm comes down slightly and marginal contact occurs with Hernangomez's (NOP) side and left arm near the wing.
Jones (NOP) lifts his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Jokic (DEN) initiates contact with Jones' (NOP) left arm and affects Jones' SQBR during the drive.
Hernangomez (NOP) goes to, not through, Morris' (DEN) space and marginal contact occurs to Morris' front as Hernangomez turns toward the basket.
Jokic (DEN) cleanly blocks Hernangomez's (NOP) layup attempt.
Hernangomez (NOP) extends his hand into Jokic's (DEN) side and delivers contact that affects Jokic's SQBR along the baseline.
Gordon (DEN) and Ingram (NOP) engage and disengage with one another as Ingram moves to set the pick.
After coming together at the same spot in the lane, McCollum's (NOP) right arm moves toward Gordon's (DEN) front and marginal contact occurs as McCollum changes direction.
McCollum (NOP) gathers the ball on his right foot and takes two steps before attempting the shot.
Gordon (DEN) moves alongside McCollum's (NOP) path and absorbs the body contact that occurs after McCollum's gather. Gordon then makes clean contact with the ball thereafter.
Jokic (DEN) makes contact with the ball after it bounces out of the imaginary cylinder above the rim.
Hernangomez (NOP) brings his hands toward Green's (DEN) back and marginal contact occurs as they each move into the lane during rebounding.
Hernangomez (NOP) and Jones (NOP) brush Jokic's (DEN) right and left arm, respectively, and marginal contact occurs after Jokic retrieves the rebound.
Replay review of the foul called on Jokic (DEN) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Jokic flails his left arm backward and initiates contact with Hernangomez's (NOP) face.
Morris (DEN) commits a take foul on Graham (NOP).
Hernangomez (NOP) and Jokic (DEN) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Forbes (DEN) firms up in his screening position in Hernangomez's (NOP) path and is bracing for the contact, which he absorbs.
Green (DEN) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Snell (NOP) during the inbound.
There is not clear and conclusive video evidence disputing that Green (DEN) touches the ball last before it goes out of bounds.
Gordon (DEN) grabs and pulls Ingram's (NOP) right arm during the inbound. The contact occurs after the release of the inbound pass.
Jokic (DEN) and Hernangomez (NOP) both enter the free throw lane prior to the release of the free throw.  The free throw attempted is whistled dead and restarted.
Hernangomez (NOP) and Jokic (DEN) engage and disengage with one another off-ball.
Jokic (DEN) brings his off-arm toward Hernangomez's (NOP) left side and marginal contact occurs as Jokic spins toward the baseline.
Hernangomez (NOP) wraps his right arm around Jokic's (DEN) upper half during the drive. The contact occurs prior to the gather and the start of Jokic's upward shooting motion.
Green (DEN) and McCollum (NOP) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Jokic (DEN) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Hernangomez (NOP) during the inbound.
Jones (NOP) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Jokic (DEN) prior to incidental contact occurring thereafter.
Ingram (NOP) moves his pivot foot heel-to-toe to create distance prior to starting his dribble.
Ingram (NOP) overtly extends his right leg and initiates contact with Green's (DEN) lower half as Green contests the jump shot attempt.
Jokic (DEN) establishes himself in a screening position in Ingram's (NOP) path and does not deliver the contact.
Green (DEN) is in the lane for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Ingram (NOP) brings his left hand toward Gordon's (DEN) front and marginal contact occurs as Ingram releases away to move beyond the perimeter.
Gordon (DEN) moves alongside Jones' (NOP) path and marginal contact occurs to Jones' side as he drives inside the lane.
Jones (NOP) slides his pivot foot after picking up his dribble inside the lane.
Ingram's (NOP) left foot steps out of bounds as he starts his dribble along the sideline.
Jones (NOP) initiates contact across Jokic's (DEN) left arm and causes Jokic to lose control of the ball after his gather inside the LDB.
Ingram (NOP) and Rivers (DEN) make marginal side-to-side contact with one another as they each pursue the rebound.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Ingram (NOP) touches the ball last before it goes out of bounds.
Jokic (DEN) establishes himself in a screening position in Jones' (NOP) path and does not deliver the contact.
Ingram (NOP) and Green (DEN) engage and disengage with one another near the wing.
Gordon (DEN) jumps vertically, maintains a legal guarding position and absorbs the body contact that occurs with Ingram (NOP) during the driving shot attempt.
McCollum (NOP) avoids making contact with Jokic (DEN) in transition.
Jones (NOP) commits a take foul on Morris (DEN).
Rivers (DEN) extends forward and initiates body contact with McCollum (NOP), affecting McCollum's SQBR.
